ent; border: 0px; font-family: a; color: transparent" class="invisible">http://www.</span><span class="visible">andadapt.com/2012/09/06</span><span style="font-size: 0px; line-height: 0; text-shadow: none; background-color: transparent; border: 0px; font-family: a; color: transparent" class="invisible">/raspberry-pi-raspbian-hfs-afp-and-time-machine/</span></a></li><li style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 5px"><strong>Tor 中继</strong>：<a style="color: #225599; text-decoration: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(225, 225, 225, 0.498039); margin: 0px 4px 0px 0px; white-space: nowrap" rel="nofollow" href="http://lifehacker.com/5953155/use-a-raspberry-pi-as-a-tor-relay-and-help-others-browser-anonymously" target="_blank" class=" external"><span style="font-size: 0px; line-height: 0; text-shadow: none; background-color: transparent; border: 0px; font-family: a; color: transparent" class="invisible">http://</span><span class="visible">lifehacker.com/5953155/</span><span style="font-size: 0px; line-height: 0; text-shadow: none; background-color: transparent; border: 0px; font-family: a; color: transparent" class="invisible">use-a-raspberry-pi-as-a-tor-relay-and-help-others-browser-anonymously</span></a></li><li style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 5px"><strong>家用 VPN 服务器：</strong><a style="color: #225599; text-decoration: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(225, 225, 225, 0.498039); margin: 0px 4px 0px 0px; white-space: nowrap" rel="nofollow" href="http://wellsb.com/post/29412820494/raspberry-pi-vpn-server" target="_blank" class=" external"><span style="font-size: 0px; line-height: 0; text-shadow: none; background-color: transparent; border: 0px; font-family: a; color: transparent" class="invisible">http://</span><span class="visible">wellsb.com/post/2941282</span><span style="font-size: 0px; line-height: 0; text-shadow: none; background-color: transparent; border: 0px; font-family: a; color: transparent" class="invisible">0494/raspberry-pi-vpn-server</span></a></l